    <summary><span data-ttu-id="11a79-101">支持基于语音合成标记语言 (SSML) 创建用于呈现文本到语音 (TTS) 的自定义引擎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-101">Supports the creation of Speech Synthesis Markup Language (SSML) based custom engines for rendering text to speech (TTS).</span></span></summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-102">命名空间的成员 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> 使 Windows 桌面语音技术支持基于语音合成标记语言（SSML）的标记语言和构造合成语音引擎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-102">The members of the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> namespace make available Windows Desktop Speech Technology support for Speech Synthesis Markup Language (SSML) based markup language and the construction of synthetic speech engines.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-103">SSML 标记语言是行业标准，提供一种基于 XML 的丰富语言，可帮助综合语音引擎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-103">The SSML markup language is the industry standard to provide a rich, XML-based language for assisting the synthetic speech engines.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11a79-104">它已由 Microsoft 和我们的竞争对手认可。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-104">It is endorsed by Microsoft and our competitors.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="11a79-105">有关 SSML 的详细信息，请参阅[语音合成标记语言规范](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=15144)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-105">For more information on SSML, see [Speech Synthesis Markup Language Specification](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=15144).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-106">使用创建新的合成语音引擎 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> 要求实现和注册从抽象基类派生的对象 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-106">Creating of a new of synthetic speech engine using <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> requires the implementation and registration of an object derived from the abstract base class <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-107"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine>通过 Windows 桌面语音技术基础结构，使用命名空间中的工具（特定对象）访问基于的综合语音引擎， <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> 应用程序决不会直接使用这些工具。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-107"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> based synthetic speech engines are accessed through Windows Desktop Speech Technology infrastructure, using the tools in the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> namespace, in particular <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> object, and are never directly used by applications.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-108">Windows 桌面语音技术基础结构可确保对传递给综合语音引擎的所有参数进行验证和线程同步。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-108">The Windows Desktop Speech Technology infrastructures ensures that all parameters passed to a synthetic speech engine are validated and thread synchronized.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="11a79-109">使用技术实现的合成语音引擎的 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-109">A of synthetic speech engine implemented using <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine> technology can:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="11a79-110">接收输入，（请参阅 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A> 、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> 、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState> 和 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SkipInfo> ）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-110">Receive input, (see <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A>,.<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.FragmentState>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SkipInfo> )</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="11a79-111">队列事件和指定操作（请参阅 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction> 、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> 、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType> 、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo> ）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-111">Queue events, and specify actions (see <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineAction>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EventParameterType>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeechEventInfo>).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="11a79-112">控制音调、说话速率和语音输出的音量（请参阅、、、、、、、、、 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ContourPoint> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ContourPointChangeType> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EmphasisBreak> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EmphasisWord> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.Prosody> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyNumber> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyPitch> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyRange> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyRate> <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyUnit> 和 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyVolume> ）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-112">Control the control the pitch, speaking rate and volume of the speech output (see <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ContourPoint>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ContourPointChangeType>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EmphasisBreak>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.EmphasisWord>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.Prosody>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyNumber>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyPitch>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyRange>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyRate>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyUnit>, and <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ProsodyVolume>)</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="11a79-113">确定语音合成的使用和输出目标（请 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SayAs> 参阅 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeakOutputFormat> ）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="11a79-113">Determine usage and output target of speech synthesis (see <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SayAs>, <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.SpeakOutputFormat>)</span></span>  
  
 ]]></format>
